{"questionId":"6acacde7-ed77-4956-a395-7f7392d6ba20_4","correctAnswer":"25","section":"Math","steps":[{"title":"Find a/b from the first equation","content":"From $\\dfrac{5a}{b}=3.5$: $\\dfrac{a}{b}=\\dfrac{3.5}{5}=0.7$."},{"title":"Combine and compute","content":"Rewrite $\\dfrac{a}{bn}=\\dfrac{a}{b}\\cdot\\dfrac{1}{n}=17.5$. Substitute: $0.7\\cdot\\dfrac{1}{n}=17.5$, so $\\dfrac{1}{n}=25$.<br/><br/>The answer is <strong>25</strong>."}]}